Most seem to agree that the line should either be drawn at Grummus, Behe, and AD, or that all mobs should be uniformly adheard to same as normal rotation mobs. So which side does everyone stand on? How do you count up the 'votes'? Does Noble Blade get the same weight on the vote as Baby Spiders or United Necro's? Obviously if you vote, somebody will win, and somebody will lose. The losers will be mad regardless of who they are, either the HoH flagged, or the wanting to be HoH flagged.<br>
<br>
Therefore it seems a COMPROMISE is in order. Each side gives in a little. So, what are the Pro teamers willing to give up, and what are the Anti teamers willing to give up? If neither are willing to give up anything we will have an impass, then voting will be required...round and round we go.<br>
