By improbable, which do you mean.  &quot;Unlikely to occur&quot; or &quot;Unlikely but true&quot;?  Because  agree with you, the very fact that on other servers peopel have teamed up into the hundreds to kill these mobs, would show that doing so is improbable (Unlikely but true).<br>
