<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Teaming between guilds is HARD. What members from guilds get to join the flagging team? What members are left off? Will those guild members left off ever now get a chance to be flagged? Who gets the dropped loot? Who decided who gets that loot?<br>
<br>
With all these questions add the difficulty of just the logistics of fighting a boss mob using the teaming process. <br>
