I would like to see AD, Behem, &amp; Grummus at least be open to teaming if needed.  I still don't think you will see alot of teaming happening.  I just don't think it applies that well to a mid-tier guild that it working to progress on it's own.  Teaming doesn't really fall into that equation.  But I still would like the opportunity to do so if the perfect teaming situation arrives.  So that if higher level people (which I am not btw - I am not fighting this battle for myself but for my guild's higher level people that I feel shouldn't have to wait for their entire guild to catch up level/gear-wise to have the opportunity to xp in a new zone) in Mid-Tier guilds that want to xp in these zones do have an outlet to do so without having to wait for their entire guild to catch up to them to then try it as a guild.  To me, this situation is about individual rights, not guild rights.<br>
